6. The 7th day of June 2024 is appointed as the day on which the following 

provisions of the Act of 2024 shall come into operation: 

(a) 

paragraph (c) of section 8(1); 

(b) paragraph (f) of section 8(1) for the purpose of the following 

payments: 

(i) 

one-parent family payment (in respect of a widow, a 
widower or a surviving civil partner); 

(ii) blind pension; 

(iii) widow’s (non-contributory) pension; 

(iv) widower’s (non-contributory) pension; 

(v) 

surviving civil partner’s (non-contributory) pension; 

(vi) guardian’s payment (non-contributory). 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

28 May, 2024. 

HEATHER HUMPHREYS, 

Minister for Social Protection. 

















